# File Organization

- main.go: rootModel, view routing, handleKey, setChildSizes
- messages.go: Msg types and tea.Cmd factories for async ops
- view_*.go: one view per file (view_table, view_info, view_create, etc.)
- styles.go: lipgloss styles, rebuildStyles(), stateColor/stateIcon
- themes.go: theme definitions, currentTheme(), setTheme()
- multipass.go: multipass CLI calls
- parsing.go: VMInfo, SnapshotInfo, parseVMInfo, parseSnapshots
